# Wasm lowering

HIR-to-Wasm ownership and HTML-Wasm boundary.

## Contract

- Input: validated HIR and companion metadata
- Output: Wasm LIR, runtime contracts and optional binary artifacts
- Decides: HIR-to-Wasm lowering, runtime capability plans and ownership projection
- Must not decide: HTML route assembly, frontend semantics
- Invariant: ownership-aware lowering preserves the GC semantic baseline

## Main paths

- `src/backends/wasm/`
- `src/projects/html_project/wasm/`
- `src/backends/wasm/hir_to_lir/ownership.rs`

